official_title: Using Entertainment Media to Deliver Educational Messages About Mammography in Saudi Arabia
inclusion_criteria:
* Saudi Arabian
* female
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 40 Years
Must have maximum age of 69 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* Females 39 or younger
* females above age 69 years
* females who have had breast cancer
* females that have had risk-reducing bilateral mastectomies
